{"tid":508742,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句Luke 根本係廢老","createTime":"2017-12-24T14:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T21:01:58.000Z","uid":89343,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fd611c2fc74e6b28b29cc3c0ac05f59ae9f57915","tid":508742,"uid":89343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:12:36.000Z","msg":"(劇透）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條友以為自己好勁學人收徒弟<br />\n一見到Ben Solo 有dark side 就淆底，決定趁人訓覺隊冧人<br />\n點知堂堂一個「legend」 咁就比達哥係咁而用force就收檔<br />\n知道自己廢就話要end Jedi 就話要死又話盛 <br />\n同拎綜援d廢老有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n最好笑下 Rey 輕鬆打低佢，Luke 訓下地下妹妹下咁求情<br />\n十足十d廢老以為自己好好抽，結果比人推兩下就訓低咋死call白車<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個退隱理由又on9，rebel 就黎全軍覆沒，自己就懶懶閒，日日渣牛奶，話知你死。<br />\n同公屋樓下d醉酒阿伯一d分別都無，係到等死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾廢老"},{"pid":"cf36333fc7c90744d12b16a5164f9f8ae669f27c","tid":508742,"uid":59485,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"有名你叫，碌撚Skywalker"},{"pid":"51108eafda524b1d85e80da2bd54b8ee3fbc6030","tid":508742,"uid":89343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T18:18:13.000Z","msg":"點解要負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7c84b4df11560300c22c3319d0793d83407190","tid":508742,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T18:26:59.000Z","msg":"正皮，條仆街真係好廢，睇到眼火爆"},{"pid":"ce00a409c6dce99b97863bfe9473ebd425d6a9d6","tid":508742,"uid":89343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T18:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正皮，條仆街真係好廢，睇到眼火爆</blockquote><br />\n一路睇一路燥，rey講極佢都唔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3890a65536914fdc296273201ce56ea50e8699c9","tid":508742,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislik